Shop for Kentucky Artisan products
The Kentucky Artisan Center at Berea presents a wide variety of Kentucky-made products, including crafts and other visual arts, music, books, and specialty food products made by over 1,000 artisans living all across the state. Products and displays at the Center change daily, with new deliveries arriving throughout the day.
If you are not able to visit our center often, you can use the products link below to enjoy new current product displays. If you would like to know more or make a purchase, call us at 859-985-5448 or email us to enjoy personal shopping assistance.
Information about many of our artists and featured Kentucky-made products can be found using the Kentucky Artisans link below. 


 

