About the Author


 


Chris Hogan
A popular and dynamic speaker on the topics of personal finance, retirement, and leadership, #1 National Best-Selling Author, Chris Hogan helps people across the country develop successful strategies to manage their money, both in their homes and businesses. For more than a decade, Hogan has served on Dave Ramsey’s team as a trusted financial coach, advisor and sought-after speaker. Hogan helps people plan for their future and reach their retirement goals through his Retire Inspired Live Events and R:IQ Assessment tool.











